import React from 'react';
import { Box, Typography, Link, Grid, List, ListItem, Divider } from '@mui/material';
import { Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn } from '@mui/icons-material';

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <Box component="footer" sx={{ bgcolor: 'background.paper', padding: 3 }}>
      <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
          <Typography variant="h6">Quick Links</Typography>
          <List>
            <ListItem><Link href="/about">About Us</Link></ListItem>
            <ListItem><Link href="/services">Services</Link></ListItem>
            <ListItem><Link href="/support">Support</Link></ListItem>
          </List>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
          <Typography variant="h6">Legal</Typography>
          <List>
            <ListItem><Link href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</Link></ListItem>
            <ListItem><Link href="/terms">Terms of Use</Link></ListItem>
          </List>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
          <Typography variant="h6">Follow Us</Typography>
          <Link href="https://www.facebook.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><Facebook /></Link>
          <Link href="https://www.twitter.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" sx={{ marginX: 1 }}><Twitter /></Link>
          <Link href="https://www.linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><LinkedIn /></Link>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>

      <Divider sx={{ my: 2 }} />

      <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" align="center">
        Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} Uninet, LLC
      </Typography>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Footer;
